Ford in $2.6bn transformation of Valencia car factory

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
US car giant Ford has spent $2.6bn (£1.7bn; €2.3bn) transforming its factory in Valencia, Spain, into what the company says is the one of the most advanced motor manufacturing plants in the world.

